      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study completed at all five operating points. GCI values for the hemolysis index ranged from 1.8% to 4.3%, meeting the < 5% criterion. Achieved gradation 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
