      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions documented with measurement uncertainty; fluid properties (viscosity, density) matched to within 5% of simulation inputs.",
      "rationale": "Flow rate and rotational speed were controlled and documented. Blood analog viscosity differed from simulation input by up to 9% at the lowest flow rate; fluid-property matching criterion not fully satisfied. Achieved gradation 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g., E_rms) computed between predicted and measured hemolysis index at each operating point; metric reported with experimental uncertainty bands.",
      "rationale": "Mean absolute error across operating points is 18% of the experimental mean; experimental uncertainty bands were reported but the comparison metric does not account for correlated measurement errors. Achieved gradation 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
