      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation input parameters (geometry, fluid properties, boundary conditions) demonstrated to be equivalent to experimental conditions within stated tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Pump geometry was digitized from CAD files with dimensional verification at five cross-sections; fluid property equivalency was partial (viscosity mismatch noted under Test Conditions factor). Equivalency formally demonstrated at three of five operating points. Achieved gradation 2."
    }
