    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The assessment team determined that the Monte Carlo UQ results, combined with the discretization error and QoI relevance factors meeting their required gradations, provide sufficient evidence to accept the model for the stated COU under conditional approval. Six factors remain one gradation below their required levels; a corrective action plan has been documented. The UQ coverage is considered adequate based on the narrative description of the screening sensitivity study in the supporting technical report, which identified inlet flow rate and tip clearance as dominant contributors. The structured sensitivity analysis record was not encoded in this package; this gap is acknowledged and scheduled for resolution in the next review cycle.",
